{"tid":568181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★術數師 評游b運程！","createTime":"2018-02-21T14:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T11:47:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"44d3d951842326bf96086111755f0f6b87b14d3b","tid":568181,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T14:12:07.000Z","msg":"楊師傅話游蕙禎如果以正格睇，衰到冇運行，逢係呢種八字正格，行到呢個運，一定冇運行，雖然仲有政治魅力，但係曇花一現，對他人會愈幫愈忙，幫人助威吶喊會反效果，今年完全冇運行，如果唔乖乖哋，會同大運對著幹，會好大壓力及吃力不討好，如果要行運要30歲後，呢3年應該閉關進修下，如果呢3年hea，3年後政治魅力都不大。而游蕙禎嘅黨友梁頌恆，楊師傅話佢行出嚟都冇政治魅力，唔好行出嚟好過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/221007_bd081f55380acd1da7288253cd1c0a66.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F221007_bd081f55380acd1da7288253cd1c0a66.png&h=229af41f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/221009_e090b5e517f3cede04485e62fdaffc08.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F221009_e090b5e517f3cede04485e62fdaffc08.png&h=4f55281c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/221010_6a8d1747ec2e6c2174a18bd61541e214.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F221010_6a8d1747ec2e6c2174a18bd61541e214.png&h=3c5989e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/221012_b599c63573d7a2a3c80d7d5c7cc87ca2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F221012_b599c63573d7a2a3c80d7d5c7cc87ca2.png&h=71cee421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180221/bkn-20180221211224034-0221_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180221%2Fbkn-20180221211224034-0221_00822_001.html&d=n5f1urfBbF4NdF4zZ9erVf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&